flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Weekly demand cycle or major event (promotion launch, product launch, significant dealer input, or executive adjustment).]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers + STREAMS - Ingest and normalize historicals, inventory, dealer signals, promotions, and product plans into the Subject Area]
  N1 --> N2[Stream: Cortex Auto Forecast + STREAMS - Generate baseline forecasts and anomaly flags using time-series models and feature engineering]
  N2 --> N3{Agent: Process Builder + Agent Team (Agentic AI) - Orchestrate Agentic reconciliation to weigh signals, surface conflicts, and propose a reconciled demand plan}
  N3 -->|Primary| N4[PB: Remote Functions + CWB Lifecycle - If confidence above threshold, finalize plan and writeback to ERP; otherwise open CWB for review]
  N4 --> N5[PB: Notification + UI Screen (Action Item / CWB view) - Notify stakeholders and collect any manual overrides or clarifications via CWB/UI]
  N5 --> N6[UI: Data View / Dashboard - Surface reconciled plan, confidence, and metric KPIs on dashboards for review and continuous learning]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: A single authoritative demand plan aligned across functions with lower stockouts and excess, improved service levels, measurable reduction in working capital tied to inventory, and auditable rationale for changes and overrides.]
  N3 -->|Low confidence or high disagreement a...| B1[Open CWB Lifecycle for cross-functional consensus review; Agent Team summarizes disagreements and recommended adjustments.]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Human-in-the-loop resolves conflicts; final plan is revised and written to SAP with recorded rationale.]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Missing or delayed dealer inputs for ...| B2[Agent Team triggers targeted dealer outreach (Action Item/Notification) and applies conservative buffer rules via Process Builder until inputs arrive.]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Temporary conservative plan reduces stockout risk; plan updates when dealer inputs received and reconciled.]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Executive urgent override or strategi...| B3[Honor executive consensus flag within reconciliation logic, log override rationale, and recalculate downstream parameters (safety stock, allocations) via Remote Functions.]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Demand plan aligns with executive priorities with auditable trail and adjusted inventory decisions.]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]